OL,3,CPolice officer guilty of raping woman
OL,5,FA West Yorkshire Police officer has
OL,6,Fbeen found guilty of raping a woman
OL,7,Fwhile off-duty.
OL,9,FPC Benjamin Bottomley, 23, was
OL,10,Fconvicted of rape and sexual assault
OL,11,Fby penetration after a trial at
OL,12,FSheffield Crown Court.
OL,14,FThe rape took place before Bottomley
OL,15,Fjoined the force. The assault occurred
OL,16,Fwhile he was a student officer.
OL,18,FBoth offences were against the same
OL,19,Fvictim and were reported to police
OL,20,Fafter he joined the force.
